<p>Dear <%= @learner.full_name.split.first %>,</p>

<p>Welcome to the UP Program!</p>

<p>We are looking forward to having you with us starting from <%= @learner.start_date.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %>.</p>

<p>Below you will find some important information regarding the beginning of your studies. Please read through it carefully and do not hesitate to contact us in case you have any questions.</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <strong>BGA Email Creation:</strong>
    <p>Attached are your BGA email credentials. Please view the tutorial document with your LCs on how to proceed with the authentication of the account. You will need your BGA email to communicate with your mentor, LCs and to keep up with all events and relevant information regarding UP!</p>
    <p>Tutorial: <a href="https://hubs.ly/Q03RhZGL0">Watch Here</a> + [Attach BGA email credentials]</p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>ETA College Credentials</strong>
    <p>Prior to your induction meeting with the ETA College team, you will receive your <strong>ETA Connect credentials</strong>. The credentials will be sent to your BGA email account, so setting up the email is a priority. The induction meeting with your Mentor will be scheduled by the Head of UP program and you will be informed of the date and time by email.</p>

    <p>Your Mentor is:</p>
    <p><%= @mentor_name %></p>
    <p>Mentor Email: <%= @mentor_email %></p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Important Contacts:</strong><br>
    <u>Learning Coaches:</u><br>
    <% @learning_coaches.each do |lc| %>
      <%= lc.full_name %> : <%= lc.email %><br>
    <% end %>
    <br>
    <u>Regional Manager:</u><br>
    <% if @regional_manager %>
      <%= @regional_manager.full_name %> : <%= @regional_manager.email %>
    <% else %>
      N/A
    <% end %>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Invitation to WhatsApp Group</strong>
    <p>We have a WhatsApp group for all UP Learners, and we encourage you to join to get to know other Learners.</p>
    <p><strong>UP Learners WhatsApp Group:</strong> <a href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/GexbP1IIMx0ICc8uAvRMDr">https://chat.whatsapp.com/GexbP1IIMx0ICc8uAvRMDr</a></p>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>We wish you all the best for the start of your Brave Journey and are pleased to welcome you to the BGA Family!</p>

<p>Kind regards,</p>
<p>BGA Admissions Team | (+351) 913 578 362</p>
